description: It´s unbelievable how much I love this job. Boys are always troubled individuals who think that the world belongs to them. Well, they are so wrong. This debtor wasn´t any exception. Lot of debts, no idea how he is gonna pay his rent and utilities. So he call me, the agent of ass penetration. He was tall, slim and I would say arrogant as well. I was waiting for the moment where i would explain him how this deal will be sealed. When I said my favorite line " ...and you are going to serve me sexually for an hour..." , he looked like a huge hammer smashed him. Haha! Full of fear, his before arrogant ass was now tight as hell. But as always, I´ve managed to get in and to teach him a lesson from home economy. DD37 : Checked!
title: Debt Dandy 37
